            <fieldText>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 109, 174); font-family: courier; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Your Form - &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/{!NewFormRecord.Id}&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 109, 174); font-family: courier; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;{!NewFormRecord.Name}&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 109, 174); font-family: courier; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt; has been cloned Successfully. Please make necessary changes before enablement.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</fieldText>
